  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Minotaur Core Replacement",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "弥诺陶洛斯核心替换组件",
    "TraditionalChinese": "彌諾陶洛斯核心替換零件"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A collection of salvaged components from a Sentinel Hardframe, reconditioned to fit the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid.<br><br>Will function as a semi-autonomous <span class=\"name name-technology\">artificial pilot plugin</span>. Installation allows the Minotaur to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">traverse planets itself</span> and engage in <span class=\"name name-stellar\">combat</span> or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">mining</span> activities to support its primary operator.<br><br>The AI pilot will always cede control to the primary operator when they enter the cockpit.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从一台护卫强化外壳上回收的构件，针对<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇进行了改装处理。<br><br>能够作为半自主<span class=\"name name-technology\">智能导航插件</span>使用。安装后，弥诺陶洛斯将能够<span class=\"name name-stellar\">独立跨越行星</span>并与敌人<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交战</span>，除此以外还能进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">采矿</span>以帮助自己的主要操作员。<br><br>当主要操作员进入驾驶舱后，人工智能驾驶员将移交设备控制权。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從巡警硬體結構中回收的一系列元件，經過翻新後用於<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇。<br><br>可作為半自主的<span class=\"name name-technology\">人工駕駛員外掛程式</span>使用。安裝後能讓彌諾陶洛斯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">獨自穿越星球</span>並進行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">戰鬥</span>或者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">採礦</span>活動，以支援其主要操作員。<br><br>主要操作員進入駕駛艙後，人工駕駛員將會交付控制權。"
  },
